  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a large skillet over medium heat.",
    "Add the tandoori chicken rest-meat and cook until browned, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the tamarind paste, garlic, ginger, paprika, cumin, salt, and black pepper. Stir to combine.",
    "Pour in the yogurt and stir to create a creamy sauce.",
    "Reduce heat to low and simmer for 10 minutes, stirring occasionally.",
    "Taste and adjust the seasoning as needed.",
    "Serve the tagine hot, garnished with additional yogurt and fresh herbs if desired."
